dct_title_s: Map of the Little Beaver Creek Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Little Beaver Creek Basin and adjacent Ohio River Tributaries
dct_description_sm: Scale bar lower right corner of map.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Little Beaver Creek Basin and quality of underground water.
